Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.94,0:00:41.92,Thai,,0,0,0,,สั่งอะไรดีคะ
Dialogue: 12,0:00:01.94,0:00:41.92,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}What would you like to order?
Dialogue: 12,0:00:38.92,0:00:41.92,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,200)}Today you'll learn 8 phrases to order food in Thai like a local.
Dialogue: 12,0:00:38.92,0:01:03.00,English,,0,0,0,,When I first moved to Bangkok, there was this noodle stall near my apartment. Every morning, the same aunty would shout at me — สั่งอะไรดีคะ — and I had no idea what to say. I just pointed at the picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:38.92,0:01:03.00,Thai,,0,0,0,,สั่งอะไรดีคะ
Dialogue: 12,0:01:00.00,0:01:03.00,English,,0,0,0,,By the end of this video, you won't need to point. You'll order in Thai, ask for recommendations, tell them how spicy you want it, and get the bill — all in Thai.
